Package: swper
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Survey-based Women emPowERment index (SWPER) 
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.0)
Author: Percy Soto-Becerra
Maintainer: Percy Soto-Becerra <percys1991@gmail.com>
Description: This packages has a variety of functions to calculate the SWPER score and derived indicators.
    Calculates the SWPER score for a given dataset and set of indices, and returns the result as a data frame.
    Categorize the SWPER score according to pre-scified cut-offs.
